
Gnome Maze Demo
---------------

This package includes copyright material and may not be used for commercial
purposes.  This software is provided as-is with no warranty of any kind and is
used at the user's own risk.

Lib dependencies:
	SDL
	SDL_image
	OpenGL
	GLU

To run on Ubuntu, required packages include:
	libsdl1.2debian
	libsd-image1.2
	libgl1-mesa-glx
	libglu1-mesa

A crude Makefile is included for building on Linux.  The -dev variants of the
packages listed above will need to be installed first.

For more info:
http://www.libsdl.org/
http://www.opengl.org/

